{"tid":430971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶]荷蘭攝影師：「舖頭貓」得香港先有！","createTime":"2017-10-10T09:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T12:57:37.000Z","uid":150685,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8972b47e8518b2fc7421d27ce9a64822402a6894","tid":430971,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「舖頭貓」絕對係香港特色</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/M-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FM-1.jpg&h=b0de60e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每隻貓咪，都是舖頭內的小皇帝！香港不少老店內都有養貓來捉老鼠，天天吃好、住好，與主人一同看舖，十分「駕勢」，也是本土的特色風景。荷蘭籍攝影師 Marcel Heijnen 為之著迷，前年開始走訪舊區，找尋「舖頭貓」蹤影，捕捉動物與小店間的微妙感情，也重新檢視我們忽略了的社區情懷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/87878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F87878.jpg&h=d416cdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/07-Copyweb-cat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F07-Copyweb-cat.jpg&h=15f63887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/08-Copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F08-Copy.jpg&h=45dd1a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/web-cat-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fweb-cat-10.jpg&h=7735fa62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F444.jpg&h=f20134fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F128.jpg&h=309d937b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/web07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fweb07.jpg&h=a544e87b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://metropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/750/pop/uploads/2017/05/web08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetropop-img.s3-website-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2F750%2Fpop%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fweb08.jpg&h=7c64fad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metropop.com.hk/%E8%88%96%E9%A0%AD%E8%B2%93-marcel-heijnen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metropop.com.hk%2F%25E8%2588%2596%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%25B2%2593-marcel-heijnen%2F&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=10ede36f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metropop.com.hk/%E8%88%96%E9%A0%AD%E8%B2%93-marcel-heijnen/</a>"},{"pid":"8bb9c2d110799ff067b1fc64f39a6af682b4f34a","tid":430971,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T11:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as